    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition car that runs and drives well enough for regular use, but it shows its age in the usual ways. Expect visible cosmetic wear, some interior aging, and minor imperfections throughout, though it still presents respectably overall and appears to have been used normally rather than abused. A solid option for someone looking for a usable older vehicle at a reasonable price, with the understanding that it is not perfect and may need typical older-car upkeep.",
