    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle offered with straightforward value in mind. This car shows its age, but it remains an appealing option for buyers seeking affordable transportation, a project, or a dependable extra vehicle without a major upfront investment. Presented honestly and priced to reflect its condition, it\u2019s a smart opportunity for someone who recognizes value where it counts.",
