      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car looking for its next owner. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts up, gets you from A to B, and could be a great budget runaround, first project, or spare vehicle for someone who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of TLC. Priced to reflect its condition, and there\u2019s still plenty of useful life here for the right buyer. If you want something affordable with potential, this one\u2019s worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid enthusiast potential. Starts, runs, and moves, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a drivetrain that feels usable as-is. The chassis presents as a good foundation for someone who wants an affordable entry point and isn\u2019t afraid of cosmetics and deferred odds-and-ends. Interior and exterior show age, but the mechanical package still offers plenty to work with. Great candidate for a budget build, weekend toy, or practical get-it-done commuter with character. Priced to reflect condition while giving the next owner a lot of platform for the money.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap, honest transportation. Runs, drives, and gets the job done. Not pretty, but priced right to move fast. Great beater, work car, or project. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that still feels ready for one more chapter. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership for someone who sees value in practicality, personality, and possibility. Great as a budget commuter, backup vehicle, or project for the right hands, it offers a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your wallet. If you appreciate a car with presence and potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows clear signs of age and wear, but offers strong value for the money and a chance to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price point. A sensible option for someone who prioritizes cost-conscious ownership.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
