      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants reliable basic transport, a practical runaround, or a project to make their own. Easy on the wallet and priced to move, it\u2019s a straightforward, honest car that could be a great fit for the right buyer. If you want something affordable and useful without spending a fortune, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong mechanical feel and plenty of upside for the next owner. Starts, runs, and offers a straightforward platform for someone who appreciates analog driving dynamics and easy wrenchability. Body and interior show age, wear, and cosmetic flaws consistent with an older used vehicle, but it presents as a complete car with good bones and a practical layout. Ideal for a budget commuter, weekend tinkering, or a build candidate for someone who wants something affordable and usable now while improving it over time. Priced to move for the right buyer who understands value in an honest driver/project.",
